  "texts": [
    "As can be seen, the BitFit method does not reach a performance comparable to that of LoRA and adaptor methods for any of languages in any of the classification scenarios.",
    "We therefore exclude this PEFT technique from our further experiments.",
    "We experiment with XLM-RoBERTa Large [35], using the following training techniques:",
    "• Full fine-tuning (FFT): All parameters of the model are updated during fine-tuning.",
    "• Low-Rank Adaptation (LoRA): The model's parameters are frozen and LoRA matrices (key, query, value) are added to both the MLP and attention layers."
  ],
